## Advanced Semantic Features

### Sentiment Analysis

Events can include sentiment information:

```json
{
  "event": "review_submitted",
  "properties": {
    "rating": 4,
    "review_text": "Great product, fast delivery!"
  },
  "sentiment": {
    "overall_score": 0.8,
    "aspects": {
      "product_quality": 0.9,
      "delivery_speed": 0.85,
      "customer_service": 0.7
    }
  }
}
```

### Supply Chain Context

Events can include supply chain information:

```json
{
  "event": "product_shipped",
  "properties": {
    "order_id": "ORD-123",
    "tracking_number": "TRK-456"
  },
  "supply_chain": {
    "fulfillment_center": "FC-WEST-01",
    "carrier": "FedEx",
    "estimated_delivery": "2024-01-18",
    "shipping_cost": 12.99,
    "carbon_footprint": 2.3
  }
}
```

### Classification and Tagging

Events support rich classification systems:

```json
{
  "event": "content_viewed",
  "properties": {
    "content_id": "ART-789",
    "content_type": "article"
  },
  "classification": {
    "topics": ["technology", "artificial_intelligence"],
    "content_tier": "premium",
    "audience_level": "expert",
    "content_format": "long_form"
  }
}
```

