### For Analytics Teams

- **Consistent Data Structure**: No more guessing about event properties
- **Rich Context**: Every event contains comprehensive business context
- **Ready-to-Use Dimensions**: Built-in segmentation and filtering capabilities
- **Cross-Platform Compatibility**: Events work across all analytics tools

### For Engineering Teams

- **Validation and Quality**: Automatic schema validation ensures data quality
- **Documentation**: Self-documenting events with clear property definitions
- **Versioning**: Schema evolution without breaking existing integrations
- **Performance**: Optimized for high-volume, real-time processing

### For Business Teams

- **Immediate Insights**: Events are designed for business understanding
- **Operational Visibility**: Real-time view into business processes
- **Customer Understanding**: Deep insights into user behavior and preferences
